ALIGNMENT & COMPLIANCE

  This software is designed in alignment with:

  • WHO Digital Health Guidelines (2019, 2024)
  • Digital Public Goods Standard (https://digitalpublicgoods.net/standard/)
  • Estratégia de Saúde Digital de Moçambique (ESD-MZ)
  • MISAU national health information system interoperability framework
  • INTIC regulatory requirements for digital platform operators
  • Mozambique Data Protection and Cybersecurity regulations

